Minimalist Clock version 1.0.1by Paul Celestin7 July 1994Copyright © 1994-1995 by Celestin Company, Inc.All rights reservedMinimalist Clock is a very small application which displays a clock on your screen. You can move the clock wherever you like. You can also view the current date by clicking the clock once.Bugs, gripes, comments, etc. should be sent to me (Paul Celestin) at one of the following addresses:Internet: celestin@celestin.comAOL and eWorld: CelestinCompuServe: 71630,650Snail mail:Paul CelestinCelestin Company, Inc.1152 Hastings AvenuePort Townsend, WA  98368